### 2. Checklist 5 Cรกch Sแปญ Dแปฅng "Sแบฃn phแบฉm Vแบญt lรฝ" (Physical Product Strategy)/ Chiแบฟn lฦฐแปฃc "Biแบฟn Tรญnh nฤng thรnh Niแปm tin" (Physical to Believability)
